，佢完全唔想答你，一嚟佢唔想笑勁你問無聊野，二嚟佢已經諗緊點班支美極返嚟。"},{"pid":"e4c30f5f4594eb0b00fae18d2c2364c252b13ed1","tid":1396353,"uid":296306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"一齊去散步又浪漫又減肥"},{"pid":"2bbbbc138a9cb71a3a3496ec23471e24fea10a6e","tid":1396353,"uid":295429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"拉佢去做gym"},{"pid":"b44f10a4dd7bdaf11cd8b14fd96ba19cd0b460ac","tid":1396353,"uid":190604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9ffbc1b094ab60903135fb44d686bc7249fd09ee","tid":1396353,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"9335bd78b6a0f4544f48e4912df36006bea5b29a","tid":1396353,"uid":59030,"like":0,"dislike":58,"score":-58,"quote":{"pid":"49d2bdedd65bd0f0d4939f230abf336b6d62c129","tid":1396353,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"佢幾多kg"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:26:04.000Z","msg":"12幾磅<br />\n17幾cm"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:27:32.000Z","msg":"我女友係 12頭 165<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n算唔算中肥 定大肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:28:05.000Z","msg":"癡撚線咁樣就叫肥<br />\n瘦又話無波<br />\n鐘意屌骨呀？"},{"pid":"5cb4377d2f306d6ad2ddf608e6a3a5f8a19fe45a","tid":1396353,"uid":292564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:30:14.000Z","msg":"屌佢啲肉"},{"pid":"c1f073142d449258f99a0243e83c075ae36ede52","tid":1396353,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:32:22.000Z","msg":"鼓勵佢參加絕食"},{"pid":"39a1cdb31af3e6556955e1a2228f5f1214402c75","tid":1396353,"uid":180422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5ccae1879eca163b02214b252a2122333f46e116","tid":1396353,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T06:17:56.000Z","msg":"17x 百二磅一d 都唔肥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:38:02.000Z","msg":"係瘦添啦"},{"pid":"1ad57a09bc20a293d378ea50277746e954